Vision Pro on an Airplane
-------------------------

I tweeted about this ( https://twitter.com/benthompson/status/1756505217913=
467324 ) , but I think it=E2=80=99s worth including in the Update as a foll=
ow-up to last week=E2=80=99s review of the Vision Pro ( https://stratechery=
