Following months of collaboration with developers in our visionOS beta prog=
ram, we=E2=80=99re excited to share that official support for visionOS is n=
ow available to all Unity Pro, Enterprise, and Industry subscribers. You ca=
n now leverage Unity=E2=80=99s familiar authoring workflows, robust XR tool=
